snippet.title: Athenian Rhapsody - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Athenian Rhapsody on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1671720/Athenian_Rhapsody

Athenian Rhapsody is a comedic RPG game with fast paced real time dodging and many other mechanics. You're given the opportunity to complete your unique Rhapsody in the world of Athens based on your interactions with the other characters, and you'll be judged on the friends or enemies you make.

Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pJWPQxgPpgE

#trailer #gametrailers #games #gaming
